thread.title: BRIEF-Ditas Dogan FY 2017 Net Result Swings To Net Profit At 4.7 Mln Lira

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Ditas Dogan FY 2017 Net Result Swings To Net Profit At 4.7 Mln Lira
text:
March 2 (Reuters) - DITAS DOGAN YEDEK PARCA:
* FY 2017 NET PROFIT AT 4.7 MILLION LIRA VERSUS NET LOSS AT 3.8 MILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* FY 2017 REVENUE AT 87.2 MILLION LIRA VERSUS 69.6 MILLION LIRA YEAR AGO
* TO PAY DIVIDEND AT NET 0,08 LIRA PER SHARE AND GROSS 0,10 LIRA PER SHARE ON APRIL 18
